t: "Na mayera wֽ»n, na mama ns־µm hunu a ־µho nni mfasoֽ» ay־µ wֽ»n ap־µde־µ, na mama wֽ»n apaepae ny־µmmoa aso (ay־µ no nsohy־µde־µ a ־µkyer־µ s־µ, saa aboa no wֽ» wֽ»n abosom), na wֽ»n asesa Onyankopֽ»n abֽ»de־µ. Obia ֽ»befiri Nyankopֽ»n akyi afa ֽ»bonsam ay־µ kyitaafoֽ» no, nokor־µ s־µ wabrװ‘ berװ‘guo a ־µda adi pefee"